source.name: Online directory of certified businesses with a detailed profile
source.description: MWBE Dataset provides a comprehensive list of certified Minority and Women-owned Business Enterprises (M/WBEs), Emerging Business Enterprises (EBEs), and or Locally-based Enterprises (LBEs) throughout the New York City tri-state area. It also provides detailed information on certified companies, including a brief description of their work history and contact information.
